    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit rebuild and rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis has been inspected for rear subframe floor hairline fractures with no defects found. The suspension retains its factory-tuned MacPherson strut/multi-link geometry, providing precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical synchronization of the drivetrain remains sharp and responsive.",
