    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2017 BMW M3 in Silverstone Metallic. This vehicle represents a perfect balance for the enthusiast who wants a driver-focused machine without the museum-piece premium. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though a discerning eye will find minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with spirited highway commutes. Inside, the Sakhir Orange Merino leather remains supple and free of tears, with the driver\u2019s side bolsters showing only light, natural creasing. Every electronic feature, from the Harman Kardon surround sound to the head-up display, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this M3 is robust; it has been serviced exclusively at certified centers, with a comprehensive service log included in the sale. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a brake fluid flush performed within the last 500 miles. The Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. It drives straight, pulls hard, and the dual-clutch transmission shifts seamlessly. This is a turn-key performance sedan ready for its next owner.",
